summary: A beautiful yet mature nord racemenu preset.
descriptionHtml:
[center][/center][center][size=6][color=#d5a6bd]Meet Tanya[/color]
[/size][size=5]My goal was to make a beautiful yet mature Nord Lady.
[img]http://s12.postimg.org/dbruz0xct/disc_image.jpg[/img][/size]
[b]
[color=#d5a6bd][font=Georgia][size=6]Requirements[/size][/font][/color][/b][size=5]
[/size][/center][center][color=#e06666][size=5]Must have[/size][/color]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/58989/?]Citrus Heads[/url][size=4] [/size][size=2](without this you have no face)[/size]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?]Brows[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu[/url]

[size=5][color=#e06666]Optional[/color]
[/size][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/72617/?]Sky female textures[/url][size=4] [/size][size=2](highly recommend this. almost a must have)[/size]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]Ks Hairdos - Renewal[/url][size=4] [/size][size=2](This is not the HDT version)[/size]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33526/?]ShowRaceMenu Precache Killer[/url][size=4] [/size][size=2](This prevents the game from crashing when opening racemenu mid game)[/size]



[color=#d5a6bd][size=6]
[b][font=Georgia]Installation[/font][/b]
[/size][/color]
[color=#e06666][size=5]Default/NMM[/size][/color]
[size=4]-Copy ''Tanya.jslot''[/size]
[size=4]-Paste it in - Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets[/size]

[color=#e06666][size=5]Mod Organizer[/size][/color]
[size=4]-Copy ''Tanya.jslot''[/size]
[size=4]-Paste it in - Mod Organizer\overwrite\skse\plugins\CharGen\Presets[/size]

[b][color=#e06666][size=5]Use ingame[/size][/color]
[/b][size=4]-Start a new game OR type ''showracemenu'' in console (without brackets)
-Once in racemenu, select a female nord.
-navigate to the preset tab on the top right.
-Hit F9 or click on load preset.
-Select Tanya[/size]





[size=3]Please note: The ENB you're using makes a huge difference in appearance.
I use Seasons of skyrim.
[/size][/center]
author: davidkarji
